column1: #The following data was exported from VDJdb: Mikhail Goncharov, Dmitry Bagaev, Dmitrii Shcherbinin, Ivan Zvyagin, Dmitry Bolotin, Paul G. Thomas, Anastasia A. Minervina, Mikhail V.
